        "content": "<p>Here are a few useful links.</p>\n<p>Tutorial website: <a href=\"https://github.com/RemyDegenne/GlimpseOfLean\">https://github.com/RemyDegenne/GlimpseOfLean</a></p>\n<p>Lean community website, with all kind of information: <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/</a><br>\nMathlib documentation (select files in the left column): <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/</a><br>\nThe new members channel on this zulip, for quick help: <a class=\"stream\" data-stream-id=\"113489\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/113489-new-members\">#new members</a> (you can also ask in this workshop channel)<br>\nMathlib github, with pull requests for new additions: <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pulls\">https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pulls</a></p>",
