    {
        "content": "<p>The question just got asked of \"how should we read mathlib theorem names\" and <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/contribute/naming.html\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/contribute/naming.html</a> describes some conventions pertaining to that</p>",
