    {
        "content": "<p>If you want to do more basic exercises to practice Lean, there are more exercise files on the tutorial repository <a href=\"https://github.com/RemyDegenne/GlimpseOfLean\">https://github.com/RemyDegenne/GlimpseOfLean</a> (see the \"Online version, no registration\" part of the readme, below the files we used yesterday)</p>",
        "id": 543787938,
